Description: Landscape with the Rest on the Flight into Egypt; the Holy Family in left foreground, ruined buildings at right. Etching
Curator's comments: The first of a set of four landscapes with the Holy Family on the Flight into Egypt (Hollstein 1 to 4).
Bibliographic references: Hollstein / German engravings, etchings and woodcuts c.1400-1700 (1)
Acquisition notes: For the history of the acquisition of the Sheepshanks collection, please see Sheepshanks.1
